## Full Feature Flow (/dx-agent-all)

**Developer types:** `/dx-agent-all <ADO-Story-ID>`

This is the master orchestrator. It chains all phases end-to-end, from ADO story to merged PR. Each phase is strictly sequential. Sub-skills run via `dx-step-executor` agents or Skill tool with `context: fork`.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph P1["Phase 1: Requirements"]
        START["ADO Story ID"]
        FETCH["1.1 /dx-req-fetch<br/>Fetch story from ADO"]
        DOR["1.1b /dx-req-dor<br/>Validate Definition of Ready"]
        DOR_GATE{"DoR score 70+?"}
        EXPLAIN["1.2 /dx-req-explain<br/>Simplify story into<br/>dev requirements"]
        RESEARCH["1.3 /dx-req-research<br/>Search codebase for<br/>related files"]
        SHARE["1.4 /dx-req-share<br/>Post team summary<br/>to ADO"]
        START --> FETCH --> DOR --> DOR_GATE
        DOR_GATE -->|pass| EXPLAIN
        EXPLAIN --> RESEARCH --> SHARE
    end

    DOR_FAIL(("PAUSE<br/>Resolve questions"))
    DOR_GATE -->|fail| DOR_FAIL

    subgraph P1E["Phase 1.5: Enrichment"]
        TICKET["/dx-ticket-analyze<br/>Deep-dive: components,<br/>files, pages"]
        FIGMA["/dx-figma-extract<br/>Extract design context,<br/>tokens, screenshots"]
        TICKET --> FIGMA
    end

    subgraph P2F["Phase 2: Figma Prototype"]
        PROTO["/dx-figma-prototype<br/>2 Haiku agents discover<br/>CSS + HTML conventions<br/>→ generate HTML/CSS prototype"]
    end

    subgraph P2["Phase 2b: Planning"]
        PLAN["2b.1 /dx-plan<br/>Generate step-by-step<br/>implementation plan<br/>(references prototype/)"]
        VALIDATE["2b.2 /dx-plan-validate<br/>Check coverage, scope,<br/>deps, reuse"]
        RESOLVE["2b.3 /dx-plan-resolve<br/>Fix flagged risks"]
        BRANCH["2b.5 ensure-feature-branch.sh<br/>Create or switch to<br/>feature branch"]
        PLAN --> VALIDATE
        VALIDATE -->|issues| RESOLVE --> VALIDATE
        VALIDATE -->|pass| BRANCH
    end

    subgraph P3["Phase 3: Execution"]
        STEP_ALL["/dx-step-all<br/>For each plan step:<br/>implement, test, review,<br/>fix, commit"]
    end

    subgraph P4["Phase 4: Build + Review"]
        BUILD["4.0 /dx-step-build<br/>Compile and deploy locally"]
        VERIFY["4.5 /dx-step-verify<br/>Lint, test, secret scan,<br/>architecture, code review"]
        HEAL["4.5-heal /dx-step-heal<br/>Auto-fix review issues<br/>max 2 cycles"]
        BUILD --> VERIFY
        VERIFY -->|fail| HEAL
        HEAL -->|fixed| VERIFY
        BUILD_FAIL["Final Summary<br/>Pipeline stops"]
        BUILD -.->|"fail"| BUILD_FAIL
    end

    subgraph P5["Phase 5: Commit + AEM"]
        COMMIT_ALL["5a /dx-step-commit<br/>Stage and commit all changes<br/>(if auto_commit enabled)"]
        SNAPSHOT["5 /aem-snapshot<br/>Record dialog fields and pages<br/>to aem-before.md"]
        AEM_VERIFY["5+ /aem-verify<br/>Compare dialog changes,<br/>create demo page"]
        COMMIT_ALL --> SNAPSHOT --> AEM_VERIFY
    end

    subgraph P6["Phase 6: Pull Request"]
        PR["6.0 /dx-pr<br/>Push branch, create<br/>ADO pull request<br/>(if auto_pr enabled)"]
    end

    subgraph P6H["Phase 6.5: Demo Capture"]
        AEM_DEMO["6.5 /aem-demo<br/>Screenshot dialog,<br/>write authoring guide"]
    end

    subgraph P7["Phase 7: Documentation"]
        DOC_AEM["7a /aem-doc-gen<br/>Full AEM documentation<br/>with screenshots"]
        DOC_GEN["7b /dx-doc-gen<br/>Generate and post<br/>wiki page"]
        SUMMARY["Final Summary<br/>Progress table"]
        DOC_AEM --> DOC_GEN --> SUMMARY
    end

    SHARE --> TICKET
    FIGMA --> PROTO
    PROTO --> PLAN
    BRANCH --> STEP_ALL
    STEP_ALL --> BUILD
    HEAL -->|pass| COMMIT_ALL
    AEM_VERIFY --> PR
    PR --> AEM_DEMO --> DOC_AEM

    style P1 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P1E fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P2F fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P2 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P3 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P4 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P5 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P6 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P6H fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style P7 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style DOR fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    style SHARE fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    style STEP_ALL fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825,color:#000
    style HEAL fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825,color:#000
    style COMMIT_ALL fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825,color:#000
    style AEM_VERIFY fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#e65100,color:#000
    style PR fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#6a1b9a,color:#000
    style DOC_AEM fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828,color:#000
    style DOC_GEN fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
```

**Key gates:**
- DoR score below 70% pauses pipeline (interactive mode)
- Plan validation FAIL = hard stop
- Build FAIL = skip review + commit + PR, jump to summary
- Verify FAIL after 2 heal cycles = skip commit, continue to summary

