## AEM Verification Flow (standalone skills)

**Developer types:** `/aem-snapshot`, `/aem-verify`, `/aem-demo`, `/aem-qa` individually as needed.

These are standalone skills invoked manually. They are NOT chained -- each reads/writes spec files independently.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph BEFORE_DEV["Before Development (manual)"]
        SNAPSHOT["/aem-snapshot<br/>Capture current dialog fields,<br/>find pages using component"]
        SNAP_OUT["aem-before.md<br/>Baseline: fields, pages,<br/>authored values"]
        SNAPSHOT --> SNAP_OUT
    end

    DEV["Developer implements changes<br/>and deploys to AEM"]

    subgraph AFTER_DEV["After Deployment (manual)"]
        VERIFY_AEM["/aem-verify<br/>Walk dialog, compare with<br/>baseline, create demo page"]
        VERIFY_IN["Reads aem-before.md<br/>(from /aem-snapshot)"]
        VERIFY_OUT["aem-after.md<br/>ADDED/REMOVED fields,<br/>demo page URL"]
        VERIFY_IN -.-> VERIFY_AEM
        VERIFY_AEM --> VERIFY_OUT
    end

    subgraph DEMO_DOC["Documentation (manual)"]
        DEMO_SKILL["/aem-demo<br/>Open AEM editor, screenshot<br/>dialog, write authoring guide"]
        DEMO_IN["Reads aem-after.md<br/>(from /aem-verify)"]
        DEMO_OUT["demo/authoring-guide.md<br/>demo/dialog-name.png"]
        DEMO_IN -.-> DEMO_SKILL
        DEMO_SKILL --> DEMO_OUT
    end

    subgraph QA_CHECK["QA (manual, requires running AEM)"]
        QA_SKILL["/aem-qa<br/>Automated QA: verify dialog,<br/>rendering, interactions"]
        BE["BE: dialog fields,<br/>JCR properties<br/>via AEM MCP"]
        FE["FE: page rendering,<br/>layout, interactions<br/>via Chrome DevTools"]
        QA_OUT["qa.json + Bug tickets<br/>if issues found"]
        QA_SKILL --> BE
        QA_SKILL --> FE
        BE --> QA_OUT
        FE --> QA_OUT
    end

    SNAP_OUT -.->|"baseline input"| VERIFY_AEM
    DEV --> VERIFY_AEM
    VERIFY_OUT -.->|"reads for page/component"| DEMO_SKILL
    QA_OUT -->|"bugs found, max 2 cycles"| DEV

    style BEFORE_DEV fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style AFTER_DEV fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style DEMO_DOC fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style QA_CHECK fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style VERIFY_AEM fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#e65100,color:#000
    style QA_SKILL fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828,color:#000
    style QA_OUT fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
```

**Key:** Dashed arrows show optional file reads, not execution chains. In `/dx-agent-all`, phases 5/5+/6.5 call these skills automatically.

