## Bug Fix Flow (/dx-bug-all)

**Developer types:** `/dx-bug-all <ADO-Bug-ID>`

Chains 3 steps via `dx-step-executor`. Step 2 (verify) can fail without blocking step 3 (fix).

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    BUG_ID["ADO Bug ID"]

    subgraph S1["Step 1: Triage"]
        TRIAGE["/dx-bug-triage<br/>Fetch bug, identify<br/>affected component"]
        FETCH_BUG["Fetch bug details<br/>from ADO"]
        FIND_COMP["Find affected files<br/>via Explore subagents"]
        TRIAGE_OUT["raw-bug.md + triage.md"]
        TRIAGE --> FETCH_BUG --> FIND_COMP --> TRIAGE_OUT
    end

    subgraph XREPO["Step 1.5: Cross-Repo Check"]
        XREPO_CHECK["Read triage.md<br/>Does fix belong to<br/>another repo?"]
        DELEGATE["Delegate to other repo<br/>STOP in this repo"]
    end

    subgraph S2["Step 2: Verify"]
        VERIFY_BUG["/dx-bug-verify<br/>Reproduce bug in browser"]
        AEM_BUG["aem-bug-executor agent<br/>Navigate AEM, follow<br/>repro steps"]
        CHROME["Chrome DevTools<br/>Screenshot evidence"]
        VERIFY_OUT["verification.md<br/>+ screenshots"]
        VERIFY_BUG --> AEM_BUG --> CHROME --> VERIFY_OUT
    end

    subgraph S3["Step 3: Fix"]
        BUG_FIX["/dx-bug-fix<br/>Plan and apply fix"]
        PLAN_BUG["Generate implement.md<br/>from triage context"]
        EXEC_BUG["Run /dx-step-all<br/>Execute fix steps"]
        PR_BUG["Run /dx-pr<br/>Create pull request"]
        BUG_FIX --> PLAN_BUG --> EXEC_BUG --> PR_BUG
    end

    subgraph LEARN["Learning"]
        BUGS_LOG[".ai/learning/raw/bugs.jsonl<br/>Bug history"]
        HOTSPOT["Hotspot detection<br/>Alert if 3+ bugs<br/>in same component"]
    end

    BUG_ID --> TRIAGE
    TRIAGE_OUT --> XREPO_CHECK
    XREPO_CHECK -->|"same repo"| VERIFY_BUG
    XREPO_CHECK -->|"other repo, pipeline mode"| DELEGATE
    VERIFY_OUT -->|"pass or fail"| BUG_FIX
    TRIAGE_OUT -->|"verify failed, use triage only"| BUG_FIX
    PR_BUG --> BUGS_LOG

    style S1 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style XREPO fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style S2 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style S3 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style LEARN fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style EXEC_BUG fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825,color:#000
    style PR_BUG fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#6a1b9a,color:#000
```

**Key:** Verify failure is non-blocking -- fix proceeds with triage data alone. Cross-repo delegation only applies in `DX_PIPELINE_MODE`.

