## Agents Summary

| Agent | Model | Invoked By | Purpose |
|-------|-------|------------|---------|
| `dx-step-executor` | Sonnet | Coordinators: req-all, step-all, bug-all, agent-all, estimate | Execute single skill in isolated context |
| `dx-pr-reviewer` | Sonnet | /dx-pr-review | Analyze PR diff, return findings with confidence 80+ filter |
| `dx-code-reviewer` | Opus | /dx-step-verify Phase 6 | Deep code review for plan alignment and quality |
| `dx-file-resolver` | Haiku | /dx-ticket-analyze, /aem-component | Find source files across repos via file-patterns.yaml |
| `dx-figma-styles` | Haiku | /dx-figma-prototype Phase A | Discover CSS/SCSS conventions (colors, breakpoints, typography, spacing) |
| `dx-figma-markup` | Haiku | /dx-figma-prototype Phase A | Discover HTML/accessibility conventions (component structure, ARIA, keyboard) |
| `dx-doc-searcher` | Haiku | /dx-help | Search .ai/ docs for architecture answers |
| `aem-inspector` | Sonnet | /aem-snapshot, /aem-verify, /aem-doc-gen | Walk dialogs, create pages, configure components via AEM MCP |
| `aem-page-finder` | Haiku | /aem-component, /aem-page-search | Find pages using a component via AEM MCP |
| `aem-demo-capture` | Sonnet | /aem-demo, /aem-doc-gen | Browser automation for dialog and rendered screenshots |
| `aem-file-resolver` | Haiku | /aem-component, /dx-ticket-analyze | Resolve component files using file-patterns.yaml |
| `aem-bug-executor` | Sonnet | /dx-bug-verify | Reproduce bugs on AEM via Chrome DevTools |

