## Project Setup (one-time, standalone)

**Developer types:** `/dx-init` once per repo. Not part of the feature flow.

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph INIT_FLOW["Initial Setup"]
        INIT["/dx-init<br/>Detect project type,<br/>scaffold .ai/ directory,<br/>generate config.yaml"]
        AEM_INIT["/aem-init<br/>Detect AEM structure,<br/>set component paths,<br/>build component index"]
        AUTO_INIT["/auto-init<br/>Scaffold automation<br/>infra for CI agents"]
        INIT --> AEM_INIT
        INIT --> AUTO_INIT
    end

    subgraph SEED["Seed Data (standalone)"]
        AEM_REFRESH["/aem-refresh<br/>Sync project knowledge<br/>from docs repo"]
    end

    style INIT_FLOW fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style SEED fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
```

**Key:** `/dx-init` calls `/aem-init` inline (step 7) when AEM is detected. `/aem-refresh` is standalone -- user runs it when seed data needs updating. It is NOT called by `/aem-init`.

