## Health and Maintenance (standalone, on-demand)

**Developer types:** `/dx-doctor`, `/aem-doctor`, or `/dx-upgrade` as needed.

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph HEALTH["Diagnostics"]
        DOCTOR["/dx-doctor<br/>Validate config, rules,<br/>scripts, MCP, seed data"]
        AEM_DOC["/aem-doctor<br/>Check component defs,<br/>OSGi, dispatcher, content"]
    end

    subgraph MAINT["Maintenance"]
        UPGRADE["/dx-upgrade<br/>Update stale plugin files,<br/>install missing deps"]
    end

    UPGRADE -->|"calls as step 0"| DOCTOR

    style HEALTH fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style MAINT fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
```

**Key:** `/dx-upgrade` calls `/dx-doctor` as step 0 to diagnose before fixing. `/aem-doctor` is fully standalone.
